# YouTube Channel Selector for NotebookLM
#
# This extension does NOT use a .env file.
# Enter your YouTube Data API v3 key in the extension's Options page
# after loading it in Chrome. The key is stored securely via chrome.storage.sync.
#
# To get an API key:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a project (or select existing)
# 3. Enable "YouTube Data API v3" in the API Library
# 4. Go to Credentials > Create Credentials > API Key
# 5. (Recommended) Restrict the key to YouTube Data API v3 only
